com.concordium.sdk.responses.blockcertificates

Class TimeoutCertificate

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.concordium.sdk.responses.blockcertificates.TimeoutCertificate

  • public class TimeoutCertificate
extends Object
    A timeout certificate is the certificate that the finalization committee issues when a round times out, thus making it possible for the protocol to proceed to the next round.
